# s安防管理优化

## 全局优化

头部栏，应加个【小人】图标，并且只显示【用户名】去除【欢迎您】

![image-20231019094157505](https://gitee.com/chen-jiujia/typora-picgo/raw/master/img/202310190941672.png)

![image-20231019094233205](https://gitee.com/chen-jiujia/typora-picgo/raw/master/img/202310190942339.png)

## APP端

1.1 查看巡查任务记录，当从下往上滑动的时候，会自动回到顶部。

![image-20231019104504769](https://gitee.com/chen-jiujia/typora-picgo/raw/master/img/202310191045811.png)

## 首页

1.1 当来访人员和来访车辆为0时，来访率应显示0%，而不是NaN%

![image-20231019094502879](https://gitee.com/chen-jiujia/typora-picgo/raw/master/img/202310190945006.png)

